		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Arrrgh. Handwriting and stickers on game cartridges is a pet peeve of mine. I mean, how hard is it to keep track of which carts belong to you? Did those kids' friends have a habit of borrowing multiple copies of the same game from different people and then mixing them up?<br /><br />Anyway, just MHO.

		

		</td>
