		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's more important to some people to be able to get the game back after lending it than to make sure the casing looks pretty.<br /><br />I'm not saying it's what I'd do, but it seems a perfectly reasonable thing to do. Did you lend games much as a kid? It's not always easy sorting it out and getting them back! Kids are very unreliable.

		

