	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Here's something that may have prompted Japanese kids to write their names on their cartridges:<br /><br />While browsing bootgod's NES Cart Database, I've noticed that the back label on Irem Famicom cartridges seems to always have a NAME blank for you to write your name in.<br /><br />If you were a kid who got an Irem cartridge and saw that NAME blank, maybe you'd think that was a good idea and put your name on all of your other cartridges too.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


