		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Whenever I buy a used game with a name Sharpied on it, I usually try to leave it intact.<br /><br />My brother said he was at a used game shop once, and found a bunch of games that used to belong to a kid he went to school with. I remember he'd always bring the extra awesome NES games over to our house, like Mega Men and Kirby's Adventure.

		

